law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 62, sec. 35. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 177, sec. 13.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Criminal and civil branches of circuit courts in counties having a population of 150,000 or more, but less than 250,000 -- Adoption of rules.
